VignetteBuilder: knitr
Description: Provides classes and methods for seismic data analysis.
        The base classes and methods are inspired by the python code
        found in the 'ObsPy' python toolbox
        <https://github.com/obspy/obspy>. Additional classes and
        methods support data returned by web services provided by the
        'IRIS DMC' <http://service.iris.edu/>.
